Basic Shortcode on VS Code
1.  Ctrl + B - Close and Reopen sidebar
2.  Ctrl + , - Open Settings
3.  Ctrl + K + arrowdown - Close Settings
4.  Ctrl + Shift + E -  Open Explorer
5.  Ctrl + Shift + F - Open Search
6.  Ctrl + Shift + G - Open Source Control
7.  Ctrl + Shift + D - Open Run / Debug
8.  Ctrl + Shift + X - Open Extension Marketplace

HTML
<h1> to <h6> - Heading level or size (The bigger the number the smaller the size).
The first line is a declaratuion statement - (<!DOCTYPE html>)
Adding a comment in html  - <!-- Comment -->
Empty element don't have closing tags e.g. - <br>

